1
00:00:00,901 --> 00:00:02,111
<font color="japanese">（司会者）あの<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>天城</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(あまぎ)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>製薬の？</c.japanese>

2
00:00:02,236 --> 00:00:03,487
<font color="japanese">（<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>冴</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(さえ)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>）狙ってます</c.japanese>

3
00:00:03,612 --> 00:00:07,074
<font color="japanese">（<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>唯</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(ゆい)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>）今すぐ誰もない
水族館にでも行って<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

4
00:00:07,199 --> 00:00:08,575
<font color="japanese">癒やされたい…</c.japanese>

5
00:00:08,700 --> 00:00:10,410
<font color="japanese">（天城）癒やしましょう
今からデートしましょう</c.japanese>

6
00:00:10,536 --> 00:00:13,288
<font color="japanese">（唯）イヤー！
（<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>名取</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(なとり)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>）フゥフゥ～ ゴーゴー ゴー</c.japanese>

7
00:00:13,956 --> 00:00:15,165
<font color="japanese">（唯）何で？</c.japanese>

8
00:00:15,833 --> 00:00:17,084
<font color="japanese">何で？</c.japanese>

9
00:00:18,335 --> 00:00:19,837
<font color="japanese">何でこうなった？</c.japanese>

10
00:00:21,380 --> 00:00:24,633
<font color="japanese">（唯）あの… お客さん
誰もいないんですけど</c.japanese>

11
00:00:24,842 --> 00:00:26,927
<font color="japanese">（天城）もちろん貸し切りました</c.japanese>

12
00:00:27,302 --> 00:00:29,930
<font color="japanese"><c.Japanese><c.Japanese>佐藤</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(さとう)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>さんが 行きたいと
つぶやいていらしたので</c.japanese>

13
00:00:30,055 --> 00:00:30,889
<font color="japanese">（唯）重っ</c.japanese>

14
00:00:31,014 --> 00:00:32,307
<font color="japanese">（天城）名取は帰っていいですよ</c.japanese>

15
00:00:32,433 --> 00:00:34,435
<font color="japanese">（名取）えっ
（天城）では 参りましょうか</c.japanese>

16
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:36,311
<font color="japanese">（冴）<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>恭一</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(きょういち)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>！</c.japanese>

17
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:39,189
<font color="japanese">（天城）冴…</c.japanese>

18
00:00:39,982 --> 00:00:41,275
<font color="japanese">名取</c.japanese>

19
00:00:41,817 --> 00:00:43,193
<font color="japanese">（名取）あ… すいません</c.japanese>

20
00:00:43,318 --> 00:00:47,865
<font color="japanese">あの… <c.Japanese><c.Japanese>三島</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(みしま)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>教授に
“社長はどこだ！”と言われまして</c.japanese>

21
00:00:47,990 --> 00:00:49,950
<font color="japanese">（唯）とりあえず助かった…</c.japanese>

22
00:00:50,909 --> 00:00:52,202
<font color="japanese">のか？</c.japanese>

23
00:00:53,495 --> 00:00:58,417
<font color="japanese">♪～</c.japanese>

24
00:02:14,076 --> 00:02:19,081
<font color="japanese">～♪</c.japanese>

25
00:02:20,290 --> 00:02:22,167
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（名取）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">いってらっしゃいませ～</c.japanese>

26
00:02:22,626 --> 00:02:26,004
{\an8}<font color="japanese">ハァ… なぜ</c.japanese><font color="japanese"><c.Japanese>藍田</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(あいだ)</c.Japanese></c.japanese><font color="japanese">も</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">いるのですか？</c.japanese>

27
00:02:26,338 --> 00:02:28,382
<font color="japanese">（藍田）冴に誘われた</c.japanese>

28
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:31,677
<font color="japanese">多能性細胞 実用化の祝いも
まだ できてないし</c.japanese>

29
00:02:31,802 --> 00:02:33,220
<font color="japanese">ちょうどいいと思って</c.japanese>

30
00:02:33,595 --> 00:02:35,430
<font color="japanese">（唯）意外と律儀</c.japanese>

31
00:02:37,975 --> 00:02:44,856
<font color="japanese">（唯）確かに 誰もいない水族館で
癒やされたいって言ったけどさ…</c.japanese>

32
00:02:51,363 --> 00:02:56,243
<font color="japanese">でもまあ 何だかんだ
癒やされちゃってるしな…</c.japanese>

33
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,999
<font color="japanese">（唯）何して…
（天城）佐藤さん</c.japanese>

34
00:03:03,417 --> 00:03:07,713
<font color="japanese">僕は 佐藤さんが望むものは
何でも…</c.japanese>

35
00:03:08,797 --> 00:03:11,425
<font color="japanese">どんなことをしてでも
僕があげたい</c.japanese>

36
00:03:12,217 --> 00:03:17,848
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんのしてほしいこと全てが
僕がしたいことになるんです</c.japanese>

37
00:03:19,391 --> 00:03:22,185
<font color="japanese">（唯）一つも
頼んではいないんだけど</c.japanese>

38
00:03:22,561 --> 00:03:24,855
<font color="japanese">若干 猟奇的なワードチョイスだけど</c.japanese>

39
00:03:26,064 --> 00:03:27,482
<font color="japanese">だけど…</c.japanese>

40
00:03:29,151 --> 00:03:31,987
<font color="japanese">この人は いつも私のこと<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

41
00:03:32,362 --> 00:03:35,407
<font color="japanese">一番に考えてはくれてるんだよね…</c.japanese>

42
00:03:36,033 --> 00:03:36,867
<font color="japanese">（冴）あーっ！</c.japanese>

43
00:03:37,993 --> 00:03:41,872
<font color="japanese">もう… なに 手とかつないで
かわいいことしてんの！</c.japanese>

44
00:03:42,914 --> 00:03:44,583
<font color="japanese">（冴）だから ダメだってば</c.japanese>

45
00:03:45,417 --> 00:03:46,835
<font color="japanese">恭一は私のだって</c.japanese>

46
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,211
<font color="japanese">冴</c.japanese>

47
00:03:48,337 --> 00:03:50,130
<font color="japanese">ペンギン見に行こ
（天城）冴…</c.japanese>

48
00:03:50,255 --> 00:03:52,716
<font color="japanese">いいから 行こっ！</c.japanese>

49
00:03:56,178 --> 00:03:57,804
<font color="japanese">（唯）行くんかい</c.japanese>

50
00:03:59,681 --> 00:04:02,100
<font color="japanese">（藍田）おう 大丈夫か？</c.japanese>

51
00:04:03,435 --> 00:04:05,437
<font color="japanese">（唯）何がですか？</c.japanese>

52
00:04:06,063 --> 00:04:07,481
<font color="japanese">藍田先生…</c.japanese>

53
00:04:08,482 --> 00:04:12,444
<font color="japanese">藍田さんこそ
お仕事 大丈夫だったんですか？</c.japanese>

54
00:04:12,569 --> 00:04:14,529
<font color="japanese">ああ 全然</c.japanese>

55
00:04:15,364 --> 00:04:17,699
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんがいるって聞いたから</c.japanese>

56
00:04:17,824 --> 00:04:18,659
<font color="japanese">（唯）え？</c.japanese>

57
00:04:18,784 --> 00:04:20,369
<font color="japanese">何となく</c.japanese>

58
00:04:20,911 --> 00:04:23,789
<font color="japanese">（唯）これは そういう意味…</c.japanese>

59
00:04:24,289 --> 00:04:28,293
<font color="japanese">ではないよね？　何となくだし</c.japanese>

60
00:04:29,378 --> 00:04:31,838
<font color="japanese">あ セイウチだ</c.japanese>

61
00:04:33,382 --> 00:04:37,177
<font color="japanese">（唯）藍田先生
いたって普通のテンションだし</c.japanese>

62
00:04:39,012 --> 00:04:43,266
<font color="japanese">えーっと…
この間は ごちそうさまでした</c.japanese>

63
00:04:43,392 --> 00:04:46,019
<font color="japanese">（藍田）ああいや こちらこそ</c.japanese>

64
00:04:46,144 --> 00:04:48,939
<font color="japanese">おもちゃ ありがとう
スヌープ お気に入り</c.japanese>

65
00:04:49,064 --> 00:04:51,316
<font color="japanese">ホントですか？　よかった</c.japanese>

66
00:04:51,441 --> 00:04:52,734
<font color="japanese">（藍田）写真ある</c.japanese>

67
00:05:00,075 --> 00:05:01,118
<font color="japanese">あ 間違えた</c.japanese>

68
00:05:01,243 --> 00:05:03,036
<font color="japanese">いや どんな間違いですか</c.japanese>

69
00:05:03,161 --> 00:05:05,706
<font color="japanese">てか プライベート
何撮ってるんですか</c.japanese>

70
00:05:06,998 --> 00:05:08,750
<font color="japanese">（藍田）あった これだ</c.japanese>

71
00:05:10,419 --> 00:05:13,755
<font color="japanese">あっ かわいい～</c.japanese>

72
00:05:15,841 --> 00:05:17,884
<font color="japanese">送ってください これ
（藍田）ああ</c.japanese>

73
00:05:18,009 --> 00:05:20,178
<font color="japanese">あっ あと これは？</c.japanese>

74
00:05:20,303 --> 00:05:23,223
<font color="japanese">（唯）かわいい
（藍田）ハハハハッ</c.japanese>

75
00:05:25,642 --> 00:05:28,895
<font color="japanese">（唯）えっ 何？
めっちゃ見てる</c.japanese>

76
00:05:29,020 --> 00:05:30,814
<font color="japanese">何？　怖い怖い…</c.japanese>

77
00:05:30,939 --> 00:05:33,692
<font color="japanese">（冴）やっぱ
誰もいない水族館っていいね</c.japanese>

78
00:05:33,942 --> 00:05:37,696
<font color="japanese">って 恭一？　なにイラついてんの</c.japanese>

79
00:05:37,821 --> 00:05:38,989
<font color="japanese">（天城）別に</c.japanese>

80
00:05:40,365 --> 00:05:41,533
<font color="japanese">（冴）ハァ…</c.japanese>

81
00:05:42,242 --> 00:05:43,452
<font color="japanese">はい あーん</c.japanese>

82
00:05:45,745 --> 00:05:46,580
<font color="japanese">あーん</c.japanese>

83
00:05:47,497 --> 00:05:49,332
<font color="japanese">はい あーん</c.japanese>

84
00:05:55,046 --> 00:05:56,256
<font color="japanese">（唯）食うんかい</c.japanese>

85
00:05:56,381 --> 00:05:59,759
<font color="japanese">（冴）にしても すごいよね</c.japanese>

86
00:05:59,885 --> 00:06:02,596
<font color="japanese">水族館 即貸し切れるなんて</c.japanese>

87
00:06:03,013 --> 00:06:04,764
<font color="japanese">さすが恭一</c.japanese>

88
00:06:05,891 --> 00:06:07,058
<font color="japanese">（天城）別に</c.japanese>

89
00:06:08,226 --> 00:06:11,521
<font color="japanese">もう！
ホント褒められ嫌いなんだから</c.japanese>

90
00:06:11,646 --> 00:06:13,148
<font color="japanese">ねえ？　佐藤さん</c.japanese>

91
00:06:14,816 --> 00:06:16,193
<font color="japanese">まあ…</c.japanese>

92
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:20,322
<font color="japanese">確かに なぜか社長って
褒められんのイヤがりますよね</c.japanese>

93
00:06:20,447 --> 00:06:22,866
<font color="japanese">（冴）あれっ 知らないの？</c.japanese>

94
00:06:24,242 --> 00:06:26,328
<font color="japanese">じゃあ 教えてあげる</c.japanese>

95
00:06:26,453 --> 00:06:28,413
<font color="japanese">恭一ってね…
（天城）冴</c.japanese>

96
00:06:33,877 --> 00:06:37,255
<font color="japanese">（唯）あの… 何ですか？</c.japanese>

97
00:06:38,006 --> 00:06:39,883
<font color="japanese">逆に気になるんですけど</c.japanese>

98
00:06:41,051 --> 00:06:43,386
<font color="japanese">（天城）佐藤さんは
知らなくてもいいことです</c.japanese>

99
00:06:44,054 --> 00:06:44,888
<font color="japanese">（唯）あ？</c.japanese>

100
00:06:47,307 --> 00:06:48,934
<font color="japanese">（冴）ちょっと待って</c.japanese>

101
00:06:49,392 --> 00:06:51,186
<font color="japanese">ねえ 恭一</c.japanese>

102
00:06:54,314 --> 00:06:55,690
<font color="japanese">どうして そんな怒るの？</c.japanese>

103
00:06:55,815 --> 00:06:59,069
<font color="japanese">怒りますよ 大体 冴は…</c.japanese>

104
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:01,696
<font color="japanese">ハァ…</c.japanese>

105
00:07:02,864 --> 00:07:05,033
<font color="japanese">まあ しかたないですね</c.japanese>

106
00:07:08,578 --> 00:07:12,541
<font color="japanese">大丈夫です 落ち着きましたから</c.japanese>

107
00:07:17,337 --> 00:07:19,756
<font color="japanese">あれは大したことじゃないの</c.japanese>

108
00:07:20,549 --> 00:07:22,175
<font color="japanese">みんなだって…</c.japanese>

109
00:07:22,300 --> 00:07:25,220
<font color="japanese">恭一のお父様だって
そう言ってたでしょう？</c.japanese>

110
00:07:25,804 --> 00:07:27,055
<font color="japanese">（天城）みんな…</c.japanese>

111
00:07:27,848 --> 00:07:29,558
<font color="japanese">だから気にしなくていいんだって</c.japanese>

112
00:07:34,104 --> 00:07:35,730
<font color="japanese">ねえ 恭一</c.japanese>

113
00:07:37,482 --> 00:07:39,734
<font color="japanese">会見でも宣言したけど…</c.japanese>

114
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:45,323
<font color="japanese">男の子たちとは
ホントに全員と別れたから</c.japanese>

115
00:07:46,366 --> 00:07:49,119
<font color="japanese">それだけ恭一に
本気になったんだからね</c.japanese>

116
00:07:50,203 --> 00:07:55,375
<font color="japanese">わかってます
会見 全部見てましたので</c.japanese>

117
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,336
<font color="japanese">冴</c.japanese>

118
00:07:59,296 --> 00:08:05,302
<font color="japanese">多能性細胞の実用化成功
本当におめでとう</c.japanese>

119
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:19,065
<font color="japanese">（男性）副作用が強い…</c.japanese>

120
00:08:19,232 --> 00:08:20,275
<font color="japanese">（男性）申し訳ありません</c.japanese>

121
00:08:23,486 --> 00:08:25,030
<font color="japanese">何 考えてんだよ</c.japanese>

122
00:08:27,073 --> 00:08:28,533
<font color="japanese">何がです</c.japanese>

123
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:33,330
<font color="japanese">恭一って
あんなに冴に流されてたっけ？</c.japanese>

124
00:08:34,122 --> 00:08:36,207
<font color="japanese">まあ 今はちょっとね</c.japanese>

125
00:08:37,250 --> 00:08:40,086
<font color="japanese">わざと冴と
仲よくしてるように見えんだけど</c.japanese>

126
00:08:40,211 --> 00:08:42,172
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんの前で
（天城）フッ</c.japanese>

127
00:08:43,298 --> 00:08:46,051
<font color="japanese">そういう見方もできますね</c.japanese>

128
00:08:46,635 --> 00:08:48,803
<font color="japanese">他にどんな見方があんだよ</c.japanese>

129
00:08:48,929 --> 00:08:50,221
<font color="japanese">藍田こそ…</c.japanese>

130
00:08:51,973 --> 00:08:54,225
<font color="japanese">何を考えているんです？</c.japanese>

131
00:08:54,351 --> 00:08:55,352
<font color="japanese">は？</c.japanese>

132
00:08:56,311 --> 00:08:59,064
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんのことが
気に入ったんですね？</c.japanese>

133
00:08:59,773 --> 00:09:00,607
<font color="japanese">はあ？</c.japanese>

134
00:09:00,732 --> 00:09:02,984
<font color="japanese">やはり無自覚でしたか</c.japanese>

135
00:09:03,568 --> 00:09:05,820
<font color="japanese">相変わらず天然ですねえ</c.japanese>

136
00:09:07,489 --> 00:09:08,949
<font color="japanese">でも ダメですよ</c.japanese>

137
00:09:09,699 --> 00:09:12,369
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんは絶対にダメです</c.japanese>

138
00:09:13,703 --> 00:09:15,622
<font color="japanese">藍田は まさかそんなこと…</c.japanese>

139
00:09:16,831 --> 00:09:18,583
<font color="japanese">しませんよね？</c.japanese>

140
00:09:24,547 --> 00:09:27,425
<font color="japanese">（冴）あの２人
何やってんだろうね</c.japanese>

141
00:09:30,428 --> 00:09:32,389
<font color="japanese">（唯）どうでもいいけど<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

142
00:09:32,514 --> 00:09:36,559
<font color="japanese">この人は社長と肩を並べるほどの
スペックを持つ女性で</c.japanese>

143
00:09:36,685 --> 00:09:39,771
<font color="japanese">どうでもいいけど 美しくて</c.japanese>

144
00:09:39,896 --> 00:09:43,650
<font color="japanese">どうでもいいけど
私の知らない社長を知ってる…</c.japanese>

145
00:09:43,817 --> 00:09:44,651
<font color="japanese">（藍田）冴</c.japanese>

146
00:09:45,026 --> 00:09:45,860
<font color="japanese">帰るぞ</c.japanese>

147
00:09:45,986 --> 00:09:48,113
<font color="japanese">はあ？　なに急に</c.japanese>

148
00:09:48,238 --> 00:09:49,322
<font color="japanese">帰るわけないし</c.japanese>

149
00:09:49,447 --> 00:09:52,617
<font color="japanese">多能性細胞の件で
ホントは忙しいんだろ 帰るぞ</c.japanese>

150
00:09:52,742 --> 00:09:55,537
<font color="japanese">（冴）ちょっと やめてよ！
痛い…</c.japanese>

151
00:09:56,705 --> 00:09:57,956
<font color="japanese">（藍田）佐藤さん</c.japanese>

152
00:09:59,082 --> 00:10:00,125
<font color="japanese">バイバイ</c.japanese>

153
00:10:01,292 --> 00:10:03,670
<font color="japanese">（唯）あ… はい
（冴）ちょっと アイちゃん！</c.japanese>

154
00:10:03,795 --> 00:10:05,672
<font color="japanese">何なのよ もう！
（唯）じゃあ また</c.japanese>

155
00:10:09,050 --> 00:10:10,593
<font color="japanese">（唯）て… え？</c.japanese>

156
00:10:10,927 --> 00:10:14,973
<font color="japanese">ちょっと待って
この状況でマンツー？</c.japanese>

157
00:10:24,941 --> 00:10:27,944
<font color="japanese">（天城）
先ほどの話は 忘れてください</c.japanese>

158
00:10:29,112 --> 00:10:31,406
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんには 話せないんです</c.japanese>

159
00:10:32,365 --> 00:10:36,619
<font color="japanese">お気になさらず
みじんも興味ありませんので</c.japanese>

160
00:10:36,745 --> 00:10:38,329
<font color="japanese">そうですか…</c.japanese>

161
00:10:39,956 --> 00:10:43,168
<font color="japanese">そういうふうには
お見受けできませんが</c.japanese>

162
00:10:45,754 --> 00:10:46,755
<font color="japanese">ん？</c.japanese>

163
00:10:51,259 --> 00:10:52,927
<font color="japanese">佐藤さん？</c.japanese>

164
00:10:53,136 --> 00:10:53,970
<font color="japanese">ハッ！</c.japanese>

165
00:11:00,977 --> 00:11:02,729
<font color="japanese">ああ…</c.japanese>

166
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:05,482
<font color="japanese">ああっ！</c.japanese>

167
00:11:06,107 --> 00:11:08,151
<font color="japanese">あああ～…</c.japanese>

168
00:11:10,195 --> 00:11:11,613
<font color="japanese">あ… 佐藤さん</c.japanese>

169
00:11:11,780 --> 00:11:15,158
<font color="japanese">ほらまた
ここでテレたりするとことかね</c.japanese>

170
00:11:15,283 --> 00:11:18,745
<font color="japanese">もう本当に 全部全部ぜーんぶ！</c.japanese>

171
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:21,581
<font color="japanese">大っ嫌いなんですよ バーカ！</c.japanese>

172
00:11:23,333 --> 00:11:24,959
<font color="japanese">送らせてください</c.japanese>

173
00:11:25,376 --> 00:11:27,962
<font color="japanese">この辺りは
電車も通っておりませんし</c.japanese>

174
00:11:28,087 --> 00:11:30,298
<font color="japanese">バスも もうありませんので</c.japanese>

175
00:11:30,965 --> 00:11:33,635
<font color="japanese">（唯）タクシー呼ぶんで
大丈夫です</c.japanese>

176
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,637
<font color="japanese">（天城）タクシーも来れませんよ</c.japanese>

177
00:11:36,721 --> 00:11:38,014
<font color="japanese">橋が工事中のために<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

178
00:11:38,139 --> 00:11:41,392
<font color="japanese">こちら方向へ来る道は
この時間 通行止めです</c.japanese>

179
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:45,438
<font color="japanese">そういう場所を選びましたから</c.japanese>

180
00:11:46,648 --> 00:11:48,775
<font color="japanese">（唯）この男…！</c.japanese>

181
00:11:49,692 --> 00:11:52,278
<font color="japanese">ねえ どうしたの？　アイちゃん</c.japanese>

182
00:11:53,238 --> 00:11:55,240
<font color="japanese">なんか おかしいよ</c.japanese>

183
00:11:56,950 --> 00:11:58,868
<font color="japanese">あのさ 冴</c.japanese>

184
00:11:58,993 --> 00:12:00,036
<font color="japanese">（冴）ん？</c.japanese>

185
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:04,457
<font color="japanese">俺って 佐藤さんのこと
気になってんの？</c.japanese>

186
00:12:05,625 --> 00:12:08,461
<font color="japanese">フッ… どう見てもそうでしょ</c.japanese>

187
00:12:10,421 --> 00:12:13,216
<font color="japanese">相変わらず天然だよね</c.japanese>

188
00:12:14,133 --> 00:12:17,095
<font color="japanese">別に恭一の彼女ってわけでも
なさそうだし</c.japanese>

189
00:12:17,470 --> 00:12:19,389
<font color="japanese">“恭一の女なら引くよ”的な？</c.japanese>

190
00:12:20,014 --> 00:12:22,767
<font color="japanese">そんなの 気にしなくていいじゃん</c.japanese>

191
00:12:22,892 --> 00:12:25,228
<font color="japanese">冴こそ 記者会見の何だあれ</c.japanese>

192
00:12:25,353 --> 00:12:27,939
<font color="japanese">あの“恭一 落とす”宣言
ああいうの やめろよ</c.japanese>

193
00:12:28,064 --> 00:12:30,900
<font color="japanese">だって言いたくなったんだもん</c.japanese>

194
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:33,987
<font color="japanese">恭一も喜んでくれると思って</c.japanese>

195
00:12:35,196 --> 00:12:39,742
<font color="japanese">ていうか 多分どの道
放っといても あの２人はね…</c.japanese>

196
00:12:40,994 --> 00:12:43,329
<font color="japanese">うまくいかないと思うよ</c.japanese>

197
00:12:44,664 --> 00:12:47,083
<font color="japanese">（唯）社長は卑怯です</c.japanese>

198
00:12:48,376 --> 00:12:53,381
<font color="japanese">いつでも 周り固めて
逃げられない状況を作って</c.japanese>

199
00:12:53,506 --> 00:12:57,176
<font color="japanese">“しょうがない”と言い訳できる
隙を与えてるところも…</c.japanese>

200
00:12:58,177 --> 00:12:59,637
<font color="japanese">タチが悪いというか</c.japanese>

201
00:12:59,762 --> 00:13:02,265
<font color="japanese">そのほうが
佐藤さんも楽になれますでしょ？</c.japanese>

202
00:13:05,768 --> 00:13:09,647
<font color="japanese">愛する佐藤さんのためなら
僕は何でもいたしますよ</c.japanese>

203
00:13:11,107 --> 00:13:13,318
<font color="japanese">だから早く佐藤さんにも<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

204
00:13:14,485 --> 00:13:17,822
<font color="japanese">僕がいないと ダメな人に
なってほしいなあ</c.japanese>

205
00:13:20,366 --> 00:13:23,953
<font color="japanese">（唯）甘やかされて
逃げ出せなくて</c.japanese>

206
00:13:26,706 --> 00:13:30,585
<font color="japanese">この人がいないと
何もできなくなって…</c.japanese>

207
00:13:31,544 --> 00:13:33,129
<font color="japanese">ダメになって</c.japanese>

208
00:13:33,671 --> 00:13:35,298
<font color="japanese">でも やめられなくて</c.japanese>

209
00:13:36,132 --> 00:13:39,594
<font color="japanese">依存みたいな 中毒みたいな</c.japanese>

210
00:13:39,719 --> 00:13:42,305
<font color="japanese">そんなドラッグみたいな関係…</c.japanese>

211
00:13:52,065 --> 00:13:54,525
<font color="japanese">（唯）私は絶対にイヤ</c.japanese>

212
00:13:55,818 --> 00:13:58,947
<font color="japanese">（天城）そんなふうに
思い始めている時点で…</c.japanese>

213
00:14:01,032 --> 00:14:03,952
<font color="japanese">すでに手遅れなんですけどねえ</c.japanese>

214
00:14:08,623 --> 00:14:11,542
<font color="japanese">（<c.Japanese><c.Japanese>麻美</c.Japanese><c.Japanese>(あみ)</c.Japanese></c.Japanese>）いや
もう そのお医者さんにしようよ</c.japanese>

215
00:14:11,668 --> 00:14:13,670
<font color="japanese">（唯）いやいや
藍田さんにも選ぶ権利が</c.japanese>

216
00:14:13,795 --> 00:14:16,631
{\an5}<font color="japanese">（麻美）
どう考えても 唯ちゃんのこと
好きだよ そのお医者さん</c.japanese>

217
00:14:16,756 --> 00:14:18,925
<font color="japanese">それに どう考えても
一般的に見て<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

218
00:14:19,050 --> 00:14:22,428
<font color="japanese">社長より
そっちのがいいと思うんだけど</c.japanese>

219
00:14:22,553 --> 00:14:24,222
<font color="japanese">ねえ？　名取</c.japanese>

220
00:14:24,347 --> 00:14:25,348
<font color="japanese">（唯）えっ？</c.japanese>

221
00:14:25,723 --> 00:14:28,601
<font color="japanese">いやまあ 俺は立場上
社長を推すけどね</c.japanese>

222
00:14:28,851 --> 00:14:31,229
<font color="japanese">てか唯ちゃんさあ
昨日 何があったの？</c.japanese>

223
00:14:31,354 --> 00:14:32,981
<font color="japanese">俺も知りたいな～</c.japanese>

224
00:14:33,106 --> 00:14:34,148
<font color="japanese">聞かせて 聞かせて</c.japanese>

225
00:14:34,524 --> 00:14:36,693
<font color="japanese">いやいや それは…</c.japanese>

226
00:14:38,569 --> 00:14:39,570
<font color="japanese">あ…</c.japanese>

227
00:14:40,571 --> 00:14:41,406
<font color="japanese">名取さん</c.japanese>

228
00:14:42,031 --> 00:14:43,950
<font color="japanese">社長って過去 何かありました？</c.japanese>

229
00:14:44,492 --> 00:14:45,410
<font color="japanese">社長の過去？</c.japanese>

230
00:14:45,910 --> 00:14:48,913
<font color="japanese">社長の褒められ嫌いの
原因ぽいんですけど</c.japanese>

231
00:14:49,205 --> 00:14:51,958
<font color="japanese">私には話したくないらしくて</c.japanese>

232
00:14:52,458 --> 00:14:55,003
<font color="japanese">そう言われると な～んか…</c.japanese>

233
00:14:55,211 --> 00:14:56,045
<font color="japanese">気になる？</c.japanese>

234
00:14:58,089 --> 00:15:01,134
<font color="japanese">（唯）かわいい～</c.japanese>

235
00:15:01,467 --> 00:15:04,262
<font color="japanese">といいつつも
犬に癒やされに来てる私</c.japanese>

236
00:15:04,387 --> 00:15:05,638
<font color="japanese">いかん いかん</c.japanese>

237
00:15:10,893 --> 00:15:11,728
<font color="japanese">（唯）あ…</c.japanese>

238
00:15:15,481 --> 00:15:17,191
<font color="japanese">おつかれさまです</c.japanese>

239
00:15:21,362 --> 00:15:22,780
<font color="japanese">おう…</c.japanese>

240
00:15:23,114 --> 00:15:26,200
<font color="japanese">またキャットフード
買いに来たんですか？</c.japanese>

241
00:15:27,452 --> 00:15:28,536
<font color="japanese">ドッグ</c.japanese>

242
00:15:29,704 --> 00:15:30,997
<font color="japanese">すいません</c.japanese>

243
00:15:31,122 --> 00:15:32,123
<font color="japanese">（携帯電話の通知音）</c.japanese>

244
00:15:39,255 --> 00:15:40,631
<font color="japanese">スヌープの？</c.japanese>

245
00:15:41,924 --> 00:15:44,052
<font color="japanese">オススメありますよ</c.japanese>

246
00:15:45,136 --> 00:15:47,638
<font color="japanese">結構 買いましたね</c.japanese>

247
00:15:48,723 --> 00:15:49,974
<font color="japanese">でも わかります</c.japanese>

248
00:15:50,099 --> 00:15:52,435
<font color="japanese">来たら
いろいろ買っちゃいますよね</c.japanese>

249
00:15:53,144 --> 00:15:54,896
<font color="japanese">車まで持ちます
（藍田）いいよ</c.japanese>

250
00:15:55,021 --> 00:15:56,147
<font color="japanese">（唯）いや 持ちます
（藍田）いや いいって</c.japanese>

251
00:15:56,272 --> 00:15:57,482
<font color="japanese">（唯）持ちます
（藍田）いいよ</c.japanese>

252
00:15:57,607 --> 00:15:59,108
<font color="japanese">（唯）持ちます 持ちます
（藍田）いいよ いいよ</c.japanese>

253
00:15:59,484 --> 00:16:00,902
<font color="japanese">（唯）持ちます
（藍田）じゃあ</c.japanese>

254
00:16:01,027 --> 00:16:02,153
<font color="japanese">（唯）離すんかい！</c.japanese>

255
00:16:05,281 --> 00:16:06,032
<font color="japanese">大丈夫か？</c.japanese>

256
00:16:06,866 --> 00:16:08,368
<font color="japanese">大丈夫です
ちょっと濡れただけなんで</c.japanese>

257
00:16:08,493 --> 00:16:10,995
<font color="japanese">風邪ひいたらアレだ 家まで送るよ</c.japanese>

258
00:16:11,120 --> 00:16:12,372
<font color="japanese">とりあえずコート
（唯）あっ いやいや</c.japanese>

259
00:16:12,497 --> 00:16:13,289
<font color="japanese">濡れてますし</c.japanese>

260
00:16:13,414 --> 00:16:15,249
<font color="japanese">そんなこと どうでもいい</c.japanese>

261
00:16:17,085 --> 00:16:19,128
<font color="japanese">（唯）あれ？　あれ？
（藍田）どうした？</c.japanese>

262
00:16:19,796 --> 00:16:23,383
<font color="japanese">（唯）いや 鍵が見当たらなくて…</c.japanese>

263
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:25,635
<font color="japanese">まあ 大丈夫です</c.japanese>

264
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:28,638
<font color="japanese">さっきのペットショップに
連絡してみるんで</c.japanese>

265
00:16:29,097 --> 00:16:31,808
<font color="japanese">今日は送ってくれて
ありがとうございました</c.japanese>

266
00:16:31,933 --> 00:16:32,892
<font color="japanese">じゃあ</c.japanese>

267
00:16:35,144 --> 00:16:38,272
<font color="japanese">外は寒いから ここで連絡しろ</c.japanese>

268
00:16:39,065 --> 00:16:40,441
<font color="japanese">はい…</c.japanese>

269
00:16:41,692 --> 00:16:44,737
<font color="japanese">（呼び出し音）</c.japanese>

270
00:16:44,862 --> 00:16:45,988
<font color="japanese">（唯）うーん</c.japanese>

271
00:16:46,572 --> 00:16:49,200
<font color="japanese">もう ペットショップ閉まってます</c.japanese>

272
00:16:50,451 --> 00:16:52,870
<font color="japanese">鍵屋さん 呼ぶしかないか</c.japanese>

273
00:16:53,913 --> 00:16:56,541
<font color="japanese">（唯）はい… はい</c.japanese>

274
00:16:56,999 --> 00:16:59,460
<font color="japanese">では よろしくお願いします</c.japanese>

275
00:17:03,589 --> 00:17:06,467
<font color="japanese">あと ２時間後くらいに
来てくれるそうです</c.japanese>

276
00:17:06,592 --> 00:17:07,885
<font color="japanese">そうか</c.japanese>

277
00:17:08,928 --> 00:17:10,471
<font color="japanese">じゃあ 私はこれで</c.japanese>

278
00:17:11,973 --> 00:17:14,016
<font color="japanese">（藍田）いや だから
どこに行くんだ</c.japanese>

279
00:17:15,435 --> 00:17:17,937
<font color="japanese">あ… ごめん</c.japanese>

280
00:17:19,856 --> 00:17:22,942
<font color="japanese">大丈夫です
どこかしらで時間 潰すんで</c.japanese>

281
00:17:23,067 --> 00:17:25,153
<font color="japanese">（藍田）服 濡れてるのに</c.japanese>

282
00:17:25,278 --> 00:17:28,614
<font color="japanese">いや でも藍田さん
激務でお疲れだろうし 申し訳…</c.japanese>

283
00:17:28,739 --> 00:17:30,283
<font color="japanese">いいから ここにいろ</c.japanese>

284
00:17:33,286 --> 00:17:35,455
<font color="japanese">ありがとうございます…</c.japanese>

285
00:17:39,083 --> 00:17:42,587
<font color="japanese">（唯）しかし 話すことねえ</c.japanese>

286
00:17:42,795 --> 00:17:44,255
<font color="japanese">藍田さん 沈黙…</c.japanese>

287
00:17:44,547 --> 00:17:45,631
<font color="japanese">寝とる！</c.japanese>

288
00:17:45,756 --> 00:17:48,968
<font color="japanese">この状況で？　やっぱ天然…</c.japanese>

289
00:17:49,886 --> 00:17:53,139
<font color="japanese">いや 激務で疲れてるのか</c.japanese>

290
00:17:59,770 --> 00:18:03,774
<font color="japanese">（携帯電話のバイブレーション）</c.japanese>

291
00:18:09,155 --> 00:18:11,908
<font color="japanese">佐藤さん 電話鳴って…</c.japanese>

292
00:18:28,716 --> 00:18:31,177
<font color="japanese">（藍田）わっ！
（唯）ヤバッ 寝てた</c.japanese>

293
00:18:31,511 --> 00:18:32,428
<font color="japanese">あ…</c.japanese>

294
00:18:37,391 --> 00:18:40,102
<font color="japanese">はい はい 佐藤です</c.japanese>

295
00:18:40,228 --> 00:18:44,023
<font color="japanese">はい よろしくお願いします
今 行きます</c.japanese>

296
00:18:47,693 --> 00:18:50,071
<font color="japanese">鍵屋さん 着いたみたいです
（藍田）ああ…</c.japanese>

297
00:18:50,196 --> 00:18:52,031
<font color="japanese">ありがとうございました</c.japanese>

298
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:54,825
<font color="japanese">あっ コートも
ありがとうございます</c.japanese>

299
00:18:54,951 --> 00:18:57,954
<font color="japanese">これ着てけよ まだ濡れてんだろ</c.japanese>

300
00:18:58,079 --> 00:18:59,747
<font color="japanese">そっちは
俺がクリーニング出しとくから</c.japanese>

301
00:19:00,122 --> 00:19:01,457
<font color="japanese">あ… いやいやいや</c.japanese>

302
00:19:01,582 --> 00:19:03,084
<font color="japanese">それぐらいさせてくれ</c.japanese>

303
00:19:05,336 --> 00:19:06,462
<font color="japanese">はい…</c.japanese>

304
00:19:06,587 --> 00:19:09,257
<font color="japanese">（藍田）そしたら返すとき
また会えるだろ</c.japanese>

305
00:19:11,425 --> 00:19:13,302
<font color="japanese">ありがとうございます…</c.japanese>

306
00:19:15,846 --> 00:19:17,557
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（携帯電話の</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">バイブレーション）</c.japanese>

307
00:19:17,557 --> 00:19:20,059
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（携帯電話の</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">バイブレーション）</c.japanese>

308
00:19:17,557 --> 00:19:20,059
<font color="japanese">また鍵屋さ… ゲッ！</c.japanese>

309
00:19:30,444 --> 00:19:33,656
<font color="japanese">（唯）とりあえず 無視しましょう</c.japanese>

310
00:19:37,368 --> 00:19:39,328
<font color="japanese">今日はありがとうございました</c.japanese>

311
00:19:39,704 --> 00:19:41,038
<font color="japanese">（ぶつかる音）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（天城）うう…</c.japanese>

312
00:19:41,372 --> 00:19:42,373
<font color="japanese">ぐはっ…</c.japanese>

313
00:19:48,754 --> 00:19:51,382
<font color="japanese">うわー 虫みたい…</c.japanese>

314
00:19:51,966 --> 00:19:55,094
<font color="japanese">藍田さん
コートもありがとうございました</c.japanese>

315
00:19:57,972 --> 00:19:59,724
<font color="japanese">（唯）邪魔
（天城）うっ！</c.japanese>

316
00:20:04,478 --> 00:20:07,315
<font color="japanese">（唯）ついてこないでください…</c.japanese>

317
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:08,274
<font color="japanese">笑顔</c.japanese>

318
00:20:09,942 --> 00:20:11,152
<font color="japanese">何ですか？</c.japanese>

319
00:20:11,694 --> 00:20:13,821
<font color="japanese">怒った顔もステキですが</c.japanese>

320
00:20:14,447 --> 00:20:17,992
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんの笑顔 僕も見たいです</c.japanese>

321
00:20:19,910 --> 00:20:22,538
<font color="japanese">（唯）あの 今
私 社長にイラついてるんですけど</c.japanese>

322
00:20:22,663 --> 00:20:23,497
<font color="japanese">なぜですか？</c.japanese>

323
00:20:23,748 --> 00:20:24,665
<font color="japanese">なぜって…</c.japanese>

324
00:20:25,207 --> 00:20:26,959
<font color="japanese">（唯）こんな所までつけてくるし</c.japanese>

325
00:20:27,084 --> 00:20:29,211
<font color="japanese">三島教授とのことも
なんかモヤるし</c.japanese>

326
00:20:29,337 --> 00:20:31,631
<font color="japanese">自分のことは教えてくれないし</c.japanese>

327
00:20:32,340 --> 00:20:33,215
<font color="japanese">ん？</c.japanese>

328
00:20:33,341 --> 00:20:35,926
<font color="japanese">それでイラつくってことは
私 社長のこと…</c.japanese>

329
00:20:36,927 --> 00:20:39,013
<font color="japanese">いいや ない！</c.japanese>

330
00:20:39,388 --> 00:20:40,848
<font color="japanese">やだ！　やだやだやだやだ</c.japanese>

331
00:20:43,017 --> 00:20:44,810
<font color="japanese">すいません 訂正します</c.japanese>

332
00:20:44,935 --> 00:20:45,770
<font color="japanese">え？</c.japanese>

333
00:20:45,895 --> 00:20:47,813
<font color="japanese">特にイラついておりません</c.japanese>

334
00:20:47,938 --> 00:20:49,148
<font color="japanese">“無”です</c.japanese>

335
00:20:49,982 --> 00:20:51,525
<font color="japanese">おつかれさまでした</c.japanese>

336
00:21:00,034 --> 00:21:01,327
<font color="japanese">（天城）つれない</c.japanese>

337
00:21:04,955 --> 00:21:07,166
<font color="japanese">（天城）佐藤さんを
家までお送りするなんて…</c.japanese>

338
00:21:10,169 --> 00:21:12,505
<font color="japanese">まあ でも僕がハッパをかければ</c.japanese>

339
00:21:13,130 --> 00:21:15,549
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんと連絡を絶つか<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

340
00:21:15,675 --> 00:21:19,011
<font color="japanese">自分の気持ちを
確認するかだとは思いましたが…</c.japanese>

341
00:21:20,513 --> 00:21:22,473
<font color="japanese">いいんですよ どちらでも</c.japanese>

342
00:21:23,557 --> 00:21:25,226
<font color="japanese">どちらにせよ<c.Japanese>―</c.Japanese></c.japanese>

343
00:21:25,518 --> 00:21:29,563
<font color="japanese">佐藤さんが 僕を意識してくれるのが
早まるだけですから</c.japanese>

344
00:21:32,650 --> 00:21:35,236
<font color="japanese">相変わらず 性悪だな</c.japanese>

345
00:21:36,237 --> 00:21:38,906
<font color="japanese">でも そっちのが
遠慮しなくていいのか</c.japanese>

346
00:21:39,031 --> 00:21:40,449
<font color="japanese">そうですね</c.japanese>

347
00:21:40,950 --> 00:21:43,994
<font color="japanese">無自覚に近づかれるより
好都合です</c.japanese>

348
00:21:45,996 --> 00:21:49,583
<font color="japanese">その調子で
早くフラれてくださいね</c.japanese>

349
00:21:51,252 --> 00:21:52,211
<font color="japanese">フフフ…</c.japanese>

350
00:21:52,962 --> 00:21:57,967
<font color="japanese">♪～</c.japanese>

351
00:22:54,190 --> 00:22:59,195
{\an8}<font color="japanese">～♪</c.japanese>

352
00:22:59,862 --> 00:23:02,698
<font color="japanese">（麻美）社長とスーパードクター
どっちにすんの？</c.japanese>

353
00:23:02,823 --> 00:23:03,616
<font color="japanese">心配？</c.japanese>

354
00:23:03,741 --> 00:23:05,493
<font color="japanese">では僕の過去をお話しすれば</c.japanese>

355
00:23:05,618 --> 00:23:07,703
<font color="japanese">藍田とお会いするのを
やめていただけますか？</c.japanese>

356
00:23:07,828 --> 00:23:11,332
<font color="japanese">（唯）社長と私は
そんな仲じゃないってことですよね？</c.japanese>

357
00:23:11,457 --> 00:23:13,626
{\an8}<font color="japanese">佐藤さんが好きです</c.japanese>

